      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning enthusiast is this 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2). Powered by the 3.6L M96 flat-six featuring VarioCam Plus, this unit delivers linear power through a precise G96 6-speed manual transaxle. The IMS bearing has been proactively addressed with a dual-row ceramic retrofit. Mechanically sound with a refreshed suspension geometry utilizing Bilstein B6 dampers for improved rebound characteristics. The cooling system has been overhauled with a high-flow water pump and low-temp thermostat to mitigate thermal stress. A robust, driver-focused example with documented service history.",
